WEBVTT

00:02:07.519 --> 00:02:08.860
That doesn't count!

00:02:09.500 --> 00:02:10.699
Ms. Cai cheated.

00:02:10.759 --> 00:02:11.960
Protest overruled.

00:02:11.960 --> 00:02:12.900
I declare...

00:02:12.939 --> 00:02:14.680
Auntie Cai wins.

00:02:16.120 --> 00:02:19.419
She advances to the final against Professor Fan.

00:02:19.419 --> 00:02:20.500
Great!

00:02:22.439 --> 00:02:23.259
Professor Fan!

00:02:23.259 --> 00:02:23.919
Auntie Cai!

00:02:23.919 --> 00:02:25.080
Come on, Professor Fan!

00:02:25.699 --> 00:02:26.639
Auntie Cai!

00:02:27.599 --> 00:02:28.419
Auntie Cai!

00:02:28.639 --> 00:02:29.400
Auntie Cai!

00:02:30.659 --> 00:02:31.539
What's going on?

00:02:31.900 --> 00:02:32.360
Calm down.

00:02:32.360 --> 00:02:33.240
Calm down. Are you okay?

00:02:35.500 --> 00:02:36.180
No need to compete.

00:02:36.520 --> 00:02:37.879
Xiao Cai is sure to be the champion.

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:39.960
Not necessarily.

00:02:39.960 --> 00:02:41.340
I'm betting on Old Fan.

00:02:42.099 --> 00:02:43.060
This expert professor...

00:02:43.060 --> 00:02:44.520
when it comes to useless things...

00:02:44.699 --> 00:02:45.680
is particularly capable.

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:48.360
I'll bet you ten bucks.

00:02:48.800 --> 00:02:49.599
You're on.

00:02:51.180 --> 00:02:51.659
Ready...

00:02:52.560 --> 00:02:52.879
Go!

00:03:07.680 --> 00:03:08.300
Mom

00:03:11.580 --> 00:03:12.199
This kid

00:03:12.979 --> 00:03:14.599
My son has come to see me

00:03:16.379 --> 00:03:17.780
What are you doing?

00:03:18.099 --> 00:03:19.680
Did Little Fox kick you out again?

00:03:19.780 --> 00:03:21.400
No, Mom, I just missed you

00:03:21.400 --> 00:03:22.699
I came over to see you

00:03:22.699 --> 00:03:24.580
Shoo, you're making it up

00:03:25.180 --> 00:03:26.259
Look at me

00:03:26.460 --> 00:03:27.159
Look at this

00:03:27.319 --> 00:03:28.099
It's not for you

00:03:28.099 --> 00:03:29.439
Toothbrush, toothpaste

00:03:29.500 --> 00:03:30.599
Undershirt, boxers

00:03:30.620 --> 00:03:32.020
Why did you bring a towel blanket too?

00:03:32.699 --> 00:03:34.159
Mom, you know how it is

00:03:34.159 --> 00:03:35.500
If I don't have this in my mouth at night

00:03:35.500 --> 00:03:36.759
I can't fall asleep

00:03:38.360 --> 00:03:39.319
How embarrassing

00:03:39.680 --> 00:03:41.000
Let's talk outside

00:03:41.039 --> 00:03:41.520
Let's go

00:03:45.699 --> 00:03:46.520
I announce

00:03:46.900 --> 00:03:48.319
for this fun activity

00:03:48.319 --> 00:03:50.039
the winner of the Staring Contest is

00:03:50.139 --> 00:03:51.580
Mr. Fan Dacheng

00:03:52.479 --> 00:03:53.199
Thank you, everyone

00:03:54.860 --> 00:03:55.580
Thank you, everyone

00:03:56.419 --> 00:03:57.020
Thank you

00:03:57.020 --> 00:03:57.879
Wait

00:04:02.900 --> 00:04:03.759
What's going on?

00:04:03.759 --> 00:04:05.080
What's wrong?

00:04:08.039 --> 00:04:08.780
Plain glasses

00:04:09.400 --> 00:04:10.060
No prescription

00:04:10.199 --> 00:04:11.419
Stop it, give me the glasses

00:04:12.280 --> 00:04:13.439
He is nearsighted

00:04:13.460 --> 00:04:14.520
Cheating

00:04:14.520 --> 00:04:16.019
When he doesn't wear glasses

00:04:16.060 --> 00:04:17.800
his eyes are no different from a blind person's

00:04:17.800 --> 00:04:18.180
Cheating

00:04:18.180 --> 00:04:19.199
This doesn't count

00:04:19.199 --> 00:04:19.839
Doesn't count

00:04:19.839 --> 00:04:22.439
Who said plain glasses aren't allowed?

00:04:22.459 --> 00:04:23.879
Hey, hand over the money

00:04:24.220 --> 00:04:25.220
He is cheating

00:04:25.220 --> 00:04:26.040
You're trying to get out of paying

00:04:26.120 --> 00:04:27.259
Referee, uphold justice

00:04:27.379 --> 00:04:27.740
Come on, take the money

00:04:27.740 --> 00:04:28.740
Referee, you need to uphold justice

00:04:28.740 --> 00:04:29.339
Money

00:04:29.420 --> 00:04:29.980
I

00:04:29.980 --> 00:04:30.819
We were just talking

00:04:30.819 --> 00:04:32.680
I'll go check on Auntie Cai first

00:04:32.939 --> 00:04:33.720
Talk later

00:04:34.139 --> 00:04:35.000
No, you can't

00:04:35.920 --> 00:04:37.740
Why did you think of wearing plain glasses?

00:04:38.439 --> 00:04:39.600
Tell the truth

00:04:39.779 --> 00:04:41.100
What is really going on?

00:04:41.459 --> 00:04:42.779
Nothing serious

00:04:42.939 --> 00:04:45.079
It's just that Xiaoli likes bamboo mats

00:04:45.139 --> 00:04:46.459
And I like grass mats

00:04:46.540 --> 00:04:47.920
So we started bickering

00:04:48.680 --> 00:04:49.899
Just over that?

00:04:49.899 --> 00:04:50.920
Was that necessary?

00:04:51.139 --> 00:04:53.439
If it's bamboo, let it be bamboo

00:04:53.639 --> 00:04:55.839
She put the bamboo mat on the floor

00:04:56.060 --> 00:04:57.279
Is it uncomfortable to sleep on?

00:04:57.279 --> 00:04:58.139
If it's uncomfortable

00:04:58.399 --> 00:05:00.000
Why put a perfectly good thing on the floor?

00:05:00.699 --> 00:05:02.000
I sleep on the floor!

00:05:02.480 --> 00:05:03.519
Where's the bed?

00:05:03.560 --> 00:05:05.060
Xiaoli and her mom sleep on the bed

00:05:05.579 --> 00:05:06.399
How come?

00:05:06.800 --> 00:05:08.439
Her mom moved into our house

00:05:08.579 --> 00:05:09.879
No, she didn't officially move in

00:05:09.959 --> 00:05:12.420
She just came to help with the kid for a few days

00:05:12.420 --> 00:05:13.240
Once the child's injury heals

00:05:13.240 --> 00:05:13.800
she'll go back

00:05:13.800 --> 00:05:14.379
What?

00:05:14.879 --> 00:05:15.920
Doudou got hurt?

00:05:16.000 --> 00:05:18.160
Nothing serious, just got hit by a car

00:05:19.860 --> 00:05:20.560
Mom

00:05:20.839 --> 00:05:21.939
Mom, why did you faint?

00:05:25.439 --> 00:05:26.759
Help!

00:05:26.800 --> 00:05:28.459
Someone come quick!

00:05:29.740 --> 00:05:31.519
Where?

00:05:31.720 --> 00:05:32.620
Where's the fire?

00:05:37.899 --> 00:05:39.939
Her blood pressure is a bit low

00:05:41.100 --> 00:05:41.959
Nothing serious

00:05:42.839 --> 00:05:43.579
She'll be fine after a rest

00:05:44.300 --> 00:05:45.120
Thank you, doctor

00:05:45.220 --> 00:05:45.759
No problem

00:05:46.120 --> 00:05:46.800
Thank you for your trouble

00:05:47.740 --> 00:05:48.899
It's my fault

00:05:49.160 --> 00:05:50.459
I spoke too fast

00:05:50.819 --> 00:05:52.379
I didn't have time to explain clearly

00:05:52.439 --> 00:05:53.560
And my mom just collapsed

00:05:54.959 --> 00:05:55.600
Actually,

00:05:55.600 --> 00:05:57.600
it was Doudou driving a toy car

00:05:57.699 --> 00:05:59.759
and crashing into another kid's toy car.

00:05:59.800 --> 00:06:01.240
He got a bump on his head.

00:06:01.959 --> 00:06:03.120
You wretched kid.

00:06:03.120 --> 00:06:04.480
You should have made that clear!

00:06:04.480 --> 00:06:05.519
Look how you scared

00:06:06.000 --> 00:06:07.220
me and your mom.

00:06:07.779 --> 00:06:09.740
So what's with the injury on your head?

00:06:10.100 --> 00:06:11.319
Didn't I just say?

00:06:11.319 --> 00:06:11.959
It was Doudou,

00:06:11.959 --> 00:06:12.379
driving a toy car...

00:06:12.379 --> 00:06:13.519
The injury on your head.

00:06:14.420 --> 00:06:15.379
Oh, this?

00:06:15.920 --> 00:06:18.300
Since Doudou got a bump on his head,

00:06:18.300 --> 00:06:19.319
my mother-in-law

00:06:19.379 --> 00:06:21.180
insisted on coming over to help for a few days.

00:06:21.339 --> 00:06:22.699
It's fine that she came,

00:06:22.699 --> 00:06:25.180
but she started nitpicking everything I did.

00:06:25.339 --> 00:06:27.759
It was Hu Xiaoli who didn't watch the kid,

00:06:28.139 --> 00:06:29.480
but she blamed it all on me.

00:06:30.240 --> 00:06:31.779
Insisted I don't care about the family.

00:06:32.139 --> 00:06:33.779
Said I don't sweep,

00:06:33.819 --> 00:06:35.540
don't do dishes, don't cook.

00:06:35.720 --> 00:06:36.680
Me, cook?

00:06:37.100 --> 00:06:38.199
When do I have time to cook?

00:06:38.319 --> 00:06:39.680
I'm so busy!

00:06:39.899 --> 00:06:40.660
Playing mahjong,

00:06:41.180 --> 00:06:42.139
playing poker,

00:06:42.360 --> 00:06:43.300
playing Fight the Landlord.

00:06:43.339 --> 00:06:45.319
Where would I find time to cook, right?

00:06:45.939 --> 00:06:47.480
As we talked, things got heated.

00:06:47.480 --> 00:06:49.100
I went straight to the kitchen without a word.

00:06:49.120 --> 00:06:50.199
I grabbed a kitchen knife.

00:06:50.660 --> 00:06:51.560
Why bring a knife into it?

00:06:51.860 --> 00:06:53.480
Let go of me.

00:06:53.699 --> 00:06:54.439
I grabbed the kitchen knife

00:06:54.439 --> 00:06:55.800
just to prove

00:06:55.920 --> 00:06:57.040
that I can cook too!

00:06:58.279 --> 00:06:59.199
And then?

00:06:59.480 --> 00:07:00.259
Then,

00:07:00.259 --> 00:07:01.779
my mother-in-law had the same reaction as you.

00:07:01.779 --> 00:07:02.899
She grabbed a frying pan

00:07:02.980 --> 00:07:03.319
and just

00:07:03.319 --> 00:07:04.639
whacked me right on the forehead.

00:07:05.899 --> 00:07:07.540
No matter how I explain, she won't listen.

00:07:07.600 --> 00:07:10.459
She insists that I attempted domestic violence.

00:07:10.920 --> 00:07:12.759
So she kicked me out.

00:07:13.920 --> 00:07:15.259
She's out of line!

00:07:15.980 --> 00:07:17.800
I can beat my own son,

00:07:18.279 --> 00:07:19.639
but no one else can.

00:07:20.199 --> 00:07:21.819
I'm going to fight her right now.

00:07:22.060 --> 00:07:23.500
Give it a rest, Auntie Cai.

00:07:24.120 --> 00:07:24.920
Dabao's actions...

00:07:24.920 --> 00:07:26.379
...really were easy to misunderstand.

00:07:27.360 --> 00:07:28.420
Well...

00:07:28.779 --> 00:07:29.500
Xiao Cai...

00:07:29.879 --> 00:07:32.000
Don't you know Dabao's personality?

00:07:32.360 --> 00:07:35.259
Would he dare grab a kitchen knife to fight someone?

00:07:35.500 --> 00:07:36.519
His mother-in-law might not know,

00:07:36.519 --> 00:07:37.860
but doesn't your wife know you?

00:07:37.920 --> 00:07:38.720
Exactly!

00:07:38.980 --> 00:07:40.399
When the old lady kicked you out,

00:07:40.399 --> 00:07:41.819
didn't your wife help you out?

00:07:41.939 --> 00:07:43.360
She did.

00:07:43.439 --> 00:07:45.360
My toothbrush and underwear...

00:07:45.360 --> 00:07:46.800
...she packed them for me.

00:07:46.800 --> 00:07:47.899
Pfft!

00:07:48.639 --> 00:07:50.279
What good is a wife like that?

00:07:50.279 --> 00:07:51.759
Divorce! Divorce immediately!

00:07:52.120 --> 00:07:53.060
Auntie Cai,

00:07:53.920 --> 00:07:54.920
you're usually the peacemaker.

00:07:54.920 --> 00:07:55.959
How can you advise a divorce?

00:07:56.480 --> 00:07:57.740
You're always saying,

00:07:57.740 --> 00:07:58.920
"A short marriage creates deep bonds."

00:07:58.920 --> 00:07:59.839
"Better to destroy ten temples..."

00:07:59.839 --> 00:08:00.819
"...than to break up one marriage."

00:08:00.819 --> 00:08:01.680
How can we not break it?

00:08:01.959 --> 00:08:03.100
His head is practically broken!

00:08:03.259 --> 00:08:04.720
And I should just swallow my anger?

00:08:04.860 --> 00:08:06.860
Uncle Liang, say something to persuade her.

00:08:06.920 --> 00:08:09.139
They're ganging up to bully us!

00:08:09.180 --> 00:08:10.459
Why wait? Divorce them!

00:08:10.959 --> 00:08:13.420
Dabao, if you don't divorce, you're not a man!

00:08:14.339 --> 00:08:15.439
All right, enough.

00:08:15.439 --> 00:08:16.680
Everyone, let's calm down first.

00:08:16.680 --> 00:08:19.040
Essentially, this is just a misunderstanding.

00:08:19.879 --> 00:08:21.980
Even if we ignore your feelings as a couple,

00:08:22.160 --> 00:08:23.439
you have to consider the child.

00:08:23.860 --> 00:08:24.860
Let me ask you, Dabao.

00:08:24.879 --> 00:08:25.079
Well,

00:08:25.079 --> 00:08:26.980
isn't your wife the one raising the child?

00:08:27.459 --> 00:08:28.939
If you divorce in the future,

00:08:29.459 --> 00:08:31.279
the court will surely award custody to her.

00:08:31.759 --> 00:08:32.299
Auntie Cai,

00:08:32.940 --> 00:08:33.519
then you won't be able to

00:08:33.519 --> 00:08:34.679
see your grandson anymore.

00:08:34.899 --> 00:08:36.080
On what grounds?

00:08:36.360 --> 00:08:37.679
Doudou's surname is Chen.

00:08:37.679 --> 00:08:38.580
So of course,

00:08:38.580 --> 00:08:39.779
custody should go to the Chen family!

00:08:39.779 --> 00:08:42.179
That's not how the law works, Auntie Cai.

00:08:42.919 --> 00:08:44.159
Who gets custody

00:08:44.220 --> 00:08:46.259
depends on who the child lives with,

00:08:46.259 --> 00:08:47.080
how old the child is,

00:08:47.080 --> 00:08:48.379
and the child's own preference.

00:08:49.559 --> 00:08:50.820
It seems you don't believe me?

00:08:51.639 --> 00:08:52.100
Fine.

00:08:52.100 --> 00:08:53.620
I'll go find the legal statutes for you.

00:08:54.899 --> 00:08:55.600
Before I get back,

00:08:55.600 --> 00:08:56.639
Auntie Cai, don't go anywhere.

00:08:58.840 --> 00:08:59.620
Hey, what?

00:09:00.259 --> 00:09:01.120
The book says,

00:09:01.980 --> 00:09:05.120
"Using fabricated facts or concealing the truth

00:09:05.159 --> 00:09:06.879
to obtain property

00:09:06.960 --> 00:09:08.000
is called fraud."

00:09:08.840 --> 00:09:10.100
Professor Fan's behavior...

00:09:10.340 --> 00:09:12.460
...I'm letting him off easy by not suing him!

00:09:12.460 --> 00:09:13.019
Mr. Li,

00:09:13.019 --> 00:09:14.759
aren't you exaggerating a bit?

00:09:14.820 --> 00:09:17.000
You just want to get out of paying that ten yuan.

00:09:17.000 --> 00:09:17.679
No, seriously.

00:09:17.679 --> 00:09:18.220
After all this talk,

00:09:18.220 --> 00:09:20.100
are you two really fighting over ten yuan?

00:09:20.320 --> 00:09:21.779
Why don't you two stop arguing?

00:09:21.779 --> 00:09:22.720
This ten yuan,

00:09:22.779 --> 00:09:23.720
I'll pay it, okay?

00:09:23.759 --> 00:09:24.480
No!

00:09:26.399 --> 00:09:27.779
Mom, don't cry.

00:09:28.019 --> 00:09:28.600
Mom!

00:09:29.000 --> 00:09:30.500
How can I not cry?

00:09:31.100 --> 00:09:33.419
Hu Xiaoli's family is bullying us!

00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:35.559
If the court awards Doudou to them,

00:09:35.559 --> 00:09:37.159
how am I supposed to live?

00:09:39.419 --> 00:09:41.360
Little Cai, don't cry yet.

00:09:41.679 --> 00:09:43.659
Didn't Dr. Chang just say...

00:09:44.059 --> 00:09:45.899
Whoever the child lives with...

00:09:45.980 --> 00:09:47.580
...is who the court will award custody to.

00:09:47.720 --> 00:09:48.740
Right, he said that.

00:09:49.320 --> 00:09:51.279
We need to strike first.

00:09:51.559 --> 00:09:52.919
Let's get the child over here first.

00:09:53.200 --> 00:09:54.779
If the child lives with you...

00:09:54.779 --> 00:09:56.360
...the court will award him to you.

00:09:56.720 --> 00:09:57.620
Right.

00:09:58.820 --> 00:10:00.779
Your Uncle Liang's idea is right.

00:10:01.139 --> 00:10:01.620
No...

00:10:01.679 --> 00:10:03.480
What time is Doudou picked up every day?

00:10:03.620 --> 00:10:04.879
Every day...

00:10:05.019 --> 00:10:06.580
How would I know?

00:10:07.539 --> 00:10:08.080
Let's go.

00:10:08.340 --> 00:10:09.840
Let's go snatch Doudou right now.

00:10:11.960 --> 00:10:13.340
Mom, will this work?

00:10:13.340 --> 00:10:14.919
You just want to anger your mom to death.

00:10:15.360 --> 00:10:16.100
At a time like this...

00:10:16.100 --> 00:10:17.100
...and you're still so spineless.

00:10:17.440 --> 00:10:18.519
Hurry up, let's go.

00:10:18.919 --> 00:10:19.399
Slow down.

00:10:19.399 --> 00:10:19.899
Slow down.

00:10:19.980 --> 00:10:21.840
Mom, are you really going?

00:10:22.179 --> 00:10:22.659
Yes.

00:10:22.659 --> 00:10:23.940
The book also said...

00:10:24.100 --> 00:10:24.539
Dr. Chang.

00:10:24.539 --> 00:10:25.059
His behavior...

00:10:25.059 --> 00:10:25.820
You're just in time.

00:10:25.820 --> 00:10:26.639
Give us your opinion.

00:10:26.659 --> 00:10:27.220
Later.

00:10:27.220 --> 00:10:28.019
I have something urgent right now.

00:10:28.360 --> 00:10:28.879
What?

00:10:29.019 --> 00:10:29.799
Old Chief.

00:10:30.059 --> 00:10:30.759
This book...

00:10:30.779 --> 00:10:31.539
I'll borrow it for a moment.

00:10:32.700 --> 00:10:33.179
What?

00:10:33.399 --> 00:10:34.299
What does this mean?

00:10:34.659 --> 00:10:36.480
He just took away my legal basis.

00:10:39.759 --> 00:10:41.139
Are you guys in cahoots?

00:10:42.360 --> 00:10:44.059
Who's in cahoots?

00:10:44.220 --> 00:10:44.840
President Li,

00:10:44.899 --> 00:10:46.740
have you developed senile paranoia?

00:10:46.759 --> 00:10:47.080
Who?

00:10:47.080 --> 00:10:47.860
Alright.

00:10:48.259 --> 00:10:48.960
I've decided.

00:10:49.279 --> 00:10:50.620
Professor Fan and Auntie Cai

00:10:50.679 --> 00:10:52.460
are joint champions of the Staring Contest.

00:10:52.659 --> 00:10:53.620
Is that acceptable now?

00:10:53.879 --> 00:10:55.700
If that's the case,

00:10:56.019 --> 00:10:56.539
President Li,

00:10:56.639 --> 00:10:57.659
give me ten yuan first.

00:10:57.720 --> 00:10:58.799
Then I'll give you ten yuan back.

00:11:00.000 --> 00:11:01.220
How can we do that?

00:11:01.820 --> 00:11:02.539
If anyone's giving money,

00:11:02.539 --> 00:11:04.500
you should give me ten yuan first,

00:11:04.639 --> 00:11:05.779
and then I'll give you ten yuan.

00:11:05.779 --> 00:11:07.120
No, it's me.

00:11:07.120 --> 00:11:07.600
Give it to me first.

00:11:07.600 --> 00:11:09.860
What's the difference?

00:11:10.039 --> 00:11:11.879
It cancels out either way.

00:11:12.460 --> 00:11:13.679
Is this really necessary?

00:11:13.860 --> 00:11:14.879
Yes, it is.

00:11:17.320 --> 00:11:19.159
Big brother, you can't go in.

00:11:19.799 --> 00:11:20.679
Brother, look here.

00:11:20.779 --> 00:11:22.259
I really am the child's parent.

00:11:22.320 --> 00:11:24.240
