Now, the key to the key issue

00:14:26.799 --> 00:14:27.320
Right

00:14:27.399 --> 00:14:28.600
So I want to test you

00:14:29.179 --> 00:14:30.899
So, the key to the key issue

00:14:31.000 --> 00:14:31.740
what is it?

