Let me tell you

00:14:35.139 --> 00:14:37.019
Are you luring the rat out of the mountain?

00:14:37.419 --> 00:14:38.500
Luring the tiger out of the mountain

00:14:38.720 --> 00:14:39.159
Luring...

00:14:41.179 --> 00:14:41.840
Don't...

00:14:41.919 --> 00:14:42.740
Don't...

00:14:42.740 --> 00:14:44.580
Teacher, look at me seriously

00:14:44.759 --> 00:14:47.100
Do I look like someone who knows a fraud gang?

00:14:48.559 --> 00:14:49.879
How could I tell that?

00:14:51.080 --> 00:14:51.779
Where is he?

00:14:53.759 --> 00:14:55.360
Hey young man, you...

00:14:55.360 --> 00:14:55.740
Come here

00:14:55.740 --> 00:14:57.019
Are you guys in cahoots?

00:15:00.700 --> 00:15:01.879
Come here, come back

00:15:01.879 --> 00:15:02.860
Is this your accomplice?

00:15:02.860 --> 00:15:03.379
Yes

00:15:03.399 --> 00:15:04.220
What accomplice?

00:15:04.220 --> 00:15:05.519
That's my mom

00:15:06.240 --> 00:15:07.200
What about your mom?

00:15:15.320 --> 00:15:15.919
Dabao

00:15:18.860 --> 00:15:20.740
The elderly don't know the law, but don't you know?

00:15:21.320 --> 00:15:23.460
Can you just steal a child back?

00:15:25.159 --> 00:15:27.220
If I hadn't gone to the police station to explain

00:15:27.779 --> 00:15:29.759
who knows how long the three of you would be detained

00:15:32.100 --> 00:15:32.899
My dear Auntie Cai

00:15:33.679 --> 00:15:34.820
my good Auntie Cai

00:15:35.899 --> 00:15:37.580
how could you be so reckless?

00:15:38.399 --> 00:15:39.940
We are all family, you...

00:15:40.559 --> 00:15:41.519
talk about family affection

00:15:41.519 --> 00:15:42.720
talk some sense

00:15:43.139 --> 00:15:44.440
Talk sense?

00:15:44.860 --> 00:15:47.179
You haven't seen that mother and daughter pair

00:15:47.559 --> 00:15:48.460
Chen Dapang

00:15:48.899 --> 00:15:51.399
You think I can't find you if you hide here?

00:15:51.559 --> 00:15:53.039
Snatching the child

00:15:53.039 --> 00:15:54.879
Auntie, watch me kill you...

00:15:54.879 --> 00:15:55.860
Hu Xiaoli, don't

00:15:55.860 --> 00:15:57.320
You dare to cause a scene here?

00:15:57.320 --> 00:15:58.120
Watch me...

00:15:58.120 --> 00:15:58.460
I...

00:15:58.460 --> 00:15:59.139
I'm dodging

00:16:04.519 --> 00:16:05.539
See that?

00:16:05.559 --> 00:16:07.759
Bullying my son right in front of my face like that.

00:16:07.759 --> 00:16:08.879
You stop right there!

00:16:08.879 --> 00:16:10.299
Stop right there, Old Cai!

00:16:11.580 --> 00:16:13.720
Are you going to handle your son abusing Xiaoli?

00:16:14.000 --> 00:16:15.879
Who's abusing whom?

00:16:15.980 --> 00:16:17.740
Everyone here saw it.

00:16:17.799 --> 00:16:19.259
Xiao Sun, you...

00:16:19.279 --> 00:16:20.779
You're twisting the facts.

00:16:20.879 --> 00:16:23.000
My daughter acted in self-defense.

00:16:23.600 --> 00:16:24.320
Ma'am...

00:16:24.500 --> 00:16:26.019
Self-defense means...

00:16:26.360 --> 00:16:28.139
during the process of him committing domestic violence...

00:16:28.139 --> 00:16:29.279
reasonable resistance is carried out.

00:16:29.279 --> 00:16:30.440
Listen to that. Only then...

00:16:31.379 --> 00:16:32.080
He said it.

00:16:32.279 --> 00:16:34.159
He was committing domestic violence against her.

00:16:34.460 --> 00:16:35.940
I was stating the legal definition.

00:16:35.940 --> 00:16:37.179
Not the factual basis.

00:16:37.460 --> 00:16:38.320
That's enough.

00:16:38.340 --> 00:16:38.879
How about this...

00:16:39.639 --> 00:16:41.320
Let me talk to this big sister.

00:16:41.519 --> 00:16:42.120
Step aside.

00:16:42.539 --> 00:16:43.440
Who are you calling "big sister"?

00:16:44.519 --> 00:16:45.639
A bunch of people with one foot in the grave,

00:16:45.639 --> 00:16:47.620
idling away in a nursing home waiting to die.

00:16:47.679 --> 00:16:48.679
And you're acting young with me?

00:16:49.700 --> 00:16:50.379
This...

00:16:50.379 --> 00:16:50.799
Ma'am...

00:16:50.799 --> 00:16:52.100
You can't say things like that.

00:16:52.120 --> 00:16:52.519
That's right.

00:16:52.519 --> 00:16:54.120
The elders come to our nursing home...

00:16:54.159 --> 00:16:55.940
to receive better care.

00:16:55.940 --> 00:16:57.019
Professional care.

00:16:57.019 --> 00:16:57.440
Wha—

00:16:57.440 --> 00:16:59.000
What do you mean "waiting to die"?

00:16:59.120 --> 00:17:00.820
Our nursing institution's mission is...

00:17:00.820 --> 00:17:01.340
To make money.

00:17:01.399 --> 00:17:01.820
That's right.

00:17:02.019 --> 00:17:02.759
No, wait.

00:17:03.580 --> 00:17:05.079
It's to serve the elderly.

00:17:05.160 --> 00:17:06.259
Then why do you charge money?

00:17:06.819 --> 00:17:09.119
That covers our reasonable operating costs.

00:17:09.180 --> 00:17:10.640
Isn't that still just to take money?

00:17:10.960 --> 00:17:11.900
Uh, Sis—

00:17:12.400 --> 00:17:13.160
Big sister...

00:17:13.279 --> 00:17:14.839
Our Willow New Town here...

00:17:14.839 --> 00:17:16.019
really doesn't charge much.

00:17:17.380 --> 00:17:19.799
Some people really do help count the cash after being sold.

00:17:19.960 --> 00:17:20.859
Forget it.

00:17:20.980 --> 00:17:22.039
Alright, I don't want to waste my breath on you...

00:17:22.039 --> 00:17:23.680
...bunch of old folks.

00:17:24.019 --> 00:17:24.920
As for me...

00:17:25.680 --> 00:17:26.579
I'm going home.

00:17:26.579 --> 00:17:29.079
To reunite with my grandson.

00:17:31.039 --> 00:17:32.299
Wait, Xiao Sun...

00:17:32.319 --> 00:17:33.019
Auntie Cai.

00:17:35.779 --> 00:17:36.440
See that?

00:17:36.980 --> 00:17:37.859
That piece of work.

00:17:38.299 --> 00:17:40.299
She was my best sister back then.

00:17:40.579 --> 00:17:42.420
In today's words, a bestie.

00:17:42.460 --> 00:17:42.920
Right?

00:17:43.940 --> 00:17:46.279
Dabao and Little Fox's childhood betrothal...

00:17:46.319 --> 00:17:47.940
was arranged by me.

00:17:48.519 --> 00:17:51.440
The key is, I didn't expect to be blinded by a fledgling.

00:17:53.000 --> 00:17:53.559
I was wrong.

00:17:54.779 --> 00:17:55.960
So you mean...

00:17:55.960 --> 00:17:57.059
our Willow New Town...

00:17:57.279 --> 00:17:58.359
won't be charging fees then?

00:17:58.420 --> 00:17:59.440
What I mean is...

00:18:00.019 --> 00:18:01.359
persuading Dabao not to divorce.

00:18:02.019 --> 00:18:02.640
I was wrong.

00:18:03.619 --> 00:18:04.299
Auntie Cai.

00:18:05.440 --> 00:18:06.339
I support you.

00:18:07.000 --> 00:18:07.859
This marriage...

00:18:09.039 --> 00:18:09.839
must end.

00:18:10.559 --> 00:18:11.880
Then my big grandson...

00:18:11.880 --> 00:18:12.519
Don't worry.

00:18:13.259 --> 00:18:15.160
Major law firms are full of my alumni.

00:18:15.619 --> 00:18:16.960
We'll use the weapon of the law...

00:18:16.960 --> 00:18:18.420
to snatch back your grandson.

00:18:18.819 --> 00:18:19.539
Right.

00:18:19.539 --> 00:18:20.559
I'll go out and check again.

00:18:20.720 --> 00:18:22.819
I'll try to goad the couple into another fight.

00:18:23.759 --> 00:18:24.900
Don't do that.

00:18:24.940 --> 00:18:27.220
My son can't beat that Little Fox.

00:18:28.019 --> 00:18:30.420
If you can't live together, you have to divorce.

00:18:30.940 --> 00:18:33.500
Enduring, dragging, stalling, suffering, stewing...

00:18:33.500 --> 00:18:34.339
Making do...

00:18:34.339 --> 00:18:35.519
is bad for everyone.

00:18:36.240 --> 00:18:37.559
Look at me, Uncle Liang, back then...

00:18:37.559 --> 00:18:38.559
when I first got divorced.

00:18:38.579 --> 00:18:40.539
It really felt awful inside.

00:18:40.680 --> 00:18:42.339
I felt uncomfortable all over.

00:18:42.799 --> 00:18:43.779
But look at me now.

00:18:44.259 --> 00:18:44.980
I'm relaxed.

00:18:45.599 --> 00:18:46.880
I'm totally relaxed.

00:18:47.140 --> 00:18:48.420
How relaxed am I!

00:18:48.619 --> 00:18:49.759
I'm free.

00:18:51.059 --> 00:18:53.440
I get up whenever I want.

00:18:53.880 --> 00:18:55.740
After getting up, I just don't fold the quilt.

00:18:56.339 --> 00:18:58.000
Dirty clothes and smelly socks thrown on the bed.

00:18:58.359 --> 00:18:59.240
One shoe, hey...

00:18:59.240 --> 00:19:00.259
lying under the bed for over half a month.

00:19:00.259 --> 00:19:01.759
I just won't fish it out.

00:19:01.759 --> 00:19:02.519
So what?

00:19:02.960 --> 00:19:03.839
Who dares to control me?

00:19:03.859 --> 00:19:04.680
That's true.

00:19:04.720 --> 00:19:06.000
Who could possibly control you?

00:19:06.960 --> 00:19:07.819
After eating...

00:19:07.819 --> 00:19:09.799
pots and pans pile up in the sink for a week.

00:19:10.380 --> 00:19:11.640
The trash in the wastebasket...

00:19:11.640 --> 00:19:13.619
has piled up into a mountain.

00:19:13.920 --> 00:19:14.900
I just won't move it.

00:19:15.160 --> 00:19:16.400
It will never disappear.

00:19:17.039 --> 00:19:19.759
When I go out, the house is a mess.

00:19:19.759 --> 00:19:20.640
A total disaster.

00:19:21.079 --> 00:19:22.079
After coming back a month later...

00:19:22.079 --> 00:19:22.799
Guess what?

00:19:22.799 --> 00:19:23.339
What?

00:19:23.720 --> 00:19:25.400
It's still a total disaster.

00:19:27.059 --> 00:19:29.700
You really can't do without someone in the house.

00:19:31.759 --> 00:19:32.240
No,

00:19:32.480 --> 00:19:34.380
I'm saying I'm happy about this.

00:19:34.420 --> 00:19:36.119
Uncle Liang, is this really happiness?

00:19:36.119 --> 00:19:38.759
No, I... I'm free now!

00:19:39.500 --> 00:19:41.359
Life is precious,

00:19:41.420 --> 00:19:43.259
but freedom is worth more.

00:19:45.140 --> 00:19:46.380
It's just that my ex-wife...

00:19:46.680 --> 00:19:48.220
Not only was her cooking bad,

00:19:48.980 --> 00:19:50.759
the main thing was she nagged too much.

00:19:51.079 --> 00:19:52.720
Her standards were too high.

00:19:52.740 --> 00:19:54.539
Every day she had to make me

00:19:54.720 --> 00:19:56.380
two meat dishes, two veggie dishes, and a soup.

00:19:56.740 --> 00:19:58.779
Staples were noodles, rice,

00:19:58.779 --> 00:20:01.460
steamed buns, stuffed buns, meat pies, pancakes,

00:20:01.579 --> 00:20:02.519
dumplings, potstickers...

00:20:02.519 --> 00:20:03.759
She never repeated a dish.

00:20:03.980 --> 00:20:05.200
How annoying is that?

00:20:05.680 --> 00:20:06.799
Look how good I have it now.

00:20:07.200 --> 00:20:08.599
Whatever flavor I want to eat,

00:20:08.640 --> 00:20:09.859
that's the flavor I eat...

00:20:10.859 --> 00:20:11.880
of instant noodles.

00:20:13.559 --> 00:20:14.859
You only eat instant noodles?

00:20:15.220 --> 00:20:16.980
Sometimes I add a ham sausage.

00:20:18.400 --> 00:20:19.160
Dabao,

00:20:19.319 --> 00:20:20.720
back then, Uncle Liang was just like you.

00:20:20.720 --> 00:20:22.259
I was a hands-off husband too.

00:20:22.819 --> 00:20:24.400
When you go to pick up the kid at kindergarten,

00:20:24.460 --> 00:20:25.160
the teacher

00:20:25.339 --> 00:20:26.259
doesn't recognize you, right?

00:20:26.420 --> 00:20:27.200
She didn't let you pick them up.

00:20:27.579 --> 00:20:28.859
I was even worse than you.

00:20:29.880 --> 00:20:31.640
Once, when I went to pick up my daughter Jingjing,

00:20:31.640 --> 00:20:33.619
I actually brought home someone else's kid.

00:20:34.500 --> 00:20:36.759
Wouldn't you say the wife would be mad?

00:20:37.380 --> 00:20:38.339
No, if you're mad,

00:20:38.339 --> 00:20:39.380
just talk to me properly.

00:20:39.380 --> 00:20:40.920
I'll change and that's it.

00:20:40.980 --> 00:20:41.599
Right?

00:20:41.640 --> 00:20:42.980
But she insisted on arguing with me.

00:20:43.019 --> 00:20:44.200
And it wasn't just her arguing.

00:20:44.200 --> 00:20:45.960
She mobilized her whole family to join in.

00:20:46.240 --> 00:20:48.180
Her dad, mom, uncle, aunt,

00:20:48.220 --> 00:20:49.859
and that wretched brother of hers.

00:20:50.220 --> 00:20:52.420
Isn't this just a gang beating?

00:20:52.559 --> 00:20:53.519
Could I tolerate that?

00:20:53.880 --> 00:20:54.319
If I tolerated that,

00:20:54.319 --> 00:20:55.859
what would happen to my status in the family?

00:20:56.079 --> 00:20:58.359
Even though I wanted to be nicer to her in my heart,

00:20:58.859 --> 00:21:00.819
I was already pushed to that point.

00:21:01.420 --> 00:21:03.220
I had to fight her.

00:21:03.400 --> 00:21:04.480
Fight to the bitter end.

00:21:06.940 --> 00:21:09.940
Who told you not to discuss it nicely with me?

00:21:10.140 --> 00:21:12.099
If you have something to say, say it nicely.

00:21:12.319 --> 00:21:13.460
Since you made such a scene,

00:21:13.940 --> 00:21:14.740
we must divorce.

00:21:14.940 --> 00:21:15.660
We have to divorce.

00:21:15.819 --> 00:21:16.799
Who's afraid of whom?

00:21:20.220 --> 00:21:21.299
Right.

00:21:21.880 --> 00:21:22.500
Xiao Cai,

00:21:22.500 --> 00:21:23.519
don't you worry.

00:21:23.920 --> 00:21:26.259
This time, I took all my years of divorce,

00:21:26.319 --> 00:21:28.400
the experience from both positive and negative sides,

00:21:28.640 --> 00:21:30.480
and explained it thoroughly to the kids.

00:21:30.960 --> 00:21:32.000
It definitely won't work out.

00:21:35.480 --> 00:21:36.440
You guys...

00:21:37.099 --> 00:21:38.539
What's the situation?

00:21:39.079 --> 00:21:39.619
Mom,

00:21:39.799 --> 00:21:40.680
Dabao and I

00:21:40.680 --> 00:21:41.779
have already made up.

00:21:41.880 --> 00:21:43.099
We're going home now.

00:21:43.259 --> 00:21:44.619
How could you make...

00:21:44.900 --> 00:21:45.759
up?

00:21:45.819 --> 00:21:46.759
Made up... good.

00:21:46.819 --> 00:21:48.460
It's good that you made up.

00:21:48.839 --> 00:21:51.440
Thanks to Uncle Liang's strong advice.

00:21:51.700 --> 00:21:53.460
You have to help the two of us

00:21:53.460 --> 00:21:55.839
thank him properly.

00:21:59.759 --> 00:22:01.339
I swear to God!

00:22:01.400 --> 00:22:03.579
I just shared my own divorce experience

00:22:03.579 --> 00:22:05.200
with the two of them.

00:22:05.440 --> 00:22:07.359
I didn't try to get them back together at all.

00:22:07.359 --> 00:22:08.319
You still won't admit it.

00:22:08.380 --> 00:22:09.619
You were the one blindly meddling.

00:22:09.700 --> 00:22:10.940
It really wasn't me blindly...

00:22:11.839 --> 00:22:12.859
I don't mean to lecture you,

00:22:12.920 --> 00:22:14.880
but it was you two mothers who blindly meddled.

00:22:15.480 --> 00:22:17.480
The young couple was just bickering,

00:22:17.480 --> 00:22:18.119
showing a bit of temper.

00:22:18.180 --> 00:22:20.519
It's just a lovers' spat that resolves itself.

00:22:20.740 --> 00:22:22.039
But you two, on the other hand...

00:22:22.099 --> 00:22:23.200
I don't mean to lecture you,

00:22:23.799 --> 00:22:24.960
and you call yourselves besties.

00:22:25.119 --> 00:22:26.660
You just protect your own kids and take sides,

00:22:26.759 --> 00:22:27.920
blowing things out of proportion.

00:22:27.940 --> 00:22:28.900
I don't mean to lecture you, I...

00:22:28.920 --> 00:22:30.740
Haven't you lectured me enough already?

00:22:31.119 --> 00:22:32.140
Grandpa Liang is right.

00:22:32.900 --> 00:22:34.079
I didn't play a helpful role either.

00:22:34.519 --> 00:22:35.400
I should reflect on that.

00:22:36.819 --> 00:22:38.500
A married couple is like a pair of binary stars,

00:22:39.200 --> 00:22:40.819
attracting and repelling each other,

00:22:40.819 --> 00:22:42.099
maintaining a dynamic equilibrium.

00:22:42.319 --> 00:22:43.859
Once the older generation gets involved,

00:22:44.140 --> 00:22:45.579
it breaks their original orbit.

00:22:45.680 --> 00:22:46.619
Their movement

00:22:46.839 --> 00:22:48.000
becomes chaotic and

00:22:48.180 --> 00:22:49.119
impossible to monitor.

00:22:49.579 --> 00:22:51.140
It's just like the three-body problem.

00:22:51.319 --> 00:22:51.859
What?

00:22:51.859 --> 00:22:52.619
What body?

00:22:52.619 --> 00:22:53.480
The Three-Body Problem.

00:22:53.839 --> 00:22:55.279
Liu Cixin's sci-fi novel.

00:22:55.500 --> 00:22:56.640
It's super popular, let me tell you.

00:22:56.759 --> 00:22:57.559
I know it.

00:22:57.799 --> 00:22:58.980
Isn't it the one where

00:23:00.019 --> 00:23:01.359
the sun is about to explode,

00:23:01.559 --> 00:23:03.220
and they have to take us Earthlings to...

00:23:03.220 --> 00:23:05.400
Taurus or Pegasus or something?

00:23:05.519 --> 00:23:06.619
Centaurus.

00:23:06.900 --> 00:23:08.700
What you're talking about is "The Wandering Earth".

00:23:08.779 --> 00:23:09.900
It's all about the same, right?

00:23:11.839 --> 00:23:13.019
Director Chang, you too,

00:23:13.380 --> 00:23:15.259
you've always supported my divorce.

00:23:15.339 --> 00:23:16.599
Why have you changed your tune now?

00:23:16.680 --> 00:23:18.140
That's why I said I need to reflect.

00:23:18.960 --> 00:23:20.160
As soon as your in-laws came over

00:23:20.160 --> 00:23:21.559
and questioned my management philosophy,

00:23:21.819 --> 00:23:22.660
I got impulsive too.

00:23:23.839 --> 00:23:24.539
Auntie Cai,

00:23:25.259 --> 00:23:26.980
matters between young people

00:23:27.440 --> 00:23:29.160
shouldn't be interfered with by the older generation.

00:23:29.579 --> 00:23:30.940
And certainly shouldn't be meddled in.

00:23:31.599 --> 00:23:32.859
So you mean

00:23:33.160 --> 00:23:34.059
that I...

00:23:34.279 --> 00:23:35.720
watching my son get bullied,

00:23:35.720 --> 00:23:37.319
should just stand by and stare helplessly?

00:23:37.480 --> 00:23:38.599
Yes, Auntie Cai.

00:23:39.079 --> 00:23:41.220
We've prepared a surprise for you.

00:23:41.680 --> 00:23:42.579
What surprise?

00:23:42.720 --> 00:23:45.059
We decided to present you with a...

00:23:52.119 --> 00:23:53.240
This is a surprise, huh?

00:23:53.960 --> 00:23:55.500
You're doing this on purpose to piss me off, right?

00:23:56.119 --> 00:23:57.019
Staring Contest?

00:23:57.079 --> 00:23:58.380
I will absolutely not accept it!

00:23:58.579 --> 00:24:00.400
I will fight them to the end!